INSTANCE.DESCRIPTION: Fetch folder name, mapping name, workflow name
INSTANCE.NAME: EXP_FETCH_MAPPING_INFO

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT USER_INFO.LOGIN_ID , USER_INFO.FIRST_NAME , USER_INFO.LAST_NAME , USER_INFO.FULL_NAME , USER_INFO.EMAIL , USER_INFO.ACTIVE_FLAG , TEAM.TEAM_NAME , TEAM.TEAM_LEADER_LOGIN_ID , USER_INFO.LAST_MODIFIED FROM $$Prefix.USER_INFO left join $$Prefix.TEAM on USER_INFO.TEAM_ID=TEAM.TEAM_ID where USER_INFO.LAST_MODIFIED > TO_TIMESTAMP ('$$last_mod_act_date', 'YYYYDDMMHH24MISSFF')

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: md5(lkp_USER_NAME || lkp_FULL_NAME || lkp_FIRST_NAME || lkp_LAST_NAME || lkp_USER_EMAIL || lkp_USER_ACTIVE)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: lkp_checksum_ui

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: md5(LOGIN_ID || FULL_NAME || FIRST_NAME || LAST_NAME || EMAIL || ACTIVE_FLAG)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: checksum_ui

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1
